fm: int minPathSum(vector<vector<int> > &grid) { 		int row = grid.size(); 		if (row == 0) return 0; 		int col = grid[0].size(); 		if (col == 0) return 0; 		vector<int> steps(col, INT_MAX); 		steps[0] = 0; 		for (int i = 0; i < row; i++) 		{ 			steps[0] = steps[0] + grid[i][0]; 			for (int j = 1; j < col; j++) 			{ 				steps[j] = min(steps[j], steps[j - 1]) + grid[i][j]; 			} 		} 		return steps[col - 1]; 	}
